{
  "stem": "214.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So I just went back to Miedzyrzec.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And there I was till May 1st, when was the deportation.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It's all in the book, what I say.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It's all in Browning's book.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And on the 3rd of May-- and we actually-- we sort of-- we didn't even hide, because, you know, my mother and I we were so-- nobody was left anymore.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You really-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But on the 3rd, I was caught.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I stuck out my head, and I was caught.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I was put in the train going to [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And that's where I was pushed out of.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, this particular-- everything is so strangely, you know, coincidental.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This particular box car, where I was in, did not have-- didn't have either the barbed wires or the bars.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was not the first body that was pushed out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was getting so absolutely-- well, we're sitting there all day long at the market, and they were shooting in.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then they finally, you know, pushed us into this train.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't even know what happened to my mother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I didn't even know where she was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was so, really, impossible.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So somebody started picking up bodies and just pushing them out to get some more room.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The Germans were standing on those steps and firing in, just for the fun of it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You have no idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "If one didn't see such-- you cannot imagine what it looked like.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So I flew out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was the middle of the night.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The train was moving.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, it was moving.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in a funny way, as I say, everything sounds so-- almost like a fairy tale.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I fell sideways into a ditch.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because, you know, along the railway.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I don't know how long I was lying.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
